     <img src="https://editor.signavio.com/p/model/4d3085a671b1414c85e306d1a26c3df5/png?inline&authkey=66fefc0917d6414e54e5af0cd763bf366821cb768de461a37d6d88393481c5f" alt="Message boundary event and reassignment service"/>
	 <h4>Note</h4>
	 This makes sense, if the engine calls a service to determine the new assignee.
  </div>
</section>

<section class="row">
  <div class="col-md-12">
